{"tid":2251384,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角警署縱火案 控方指12港人之一黃臨福想殺警","createTime":"2020-10-20T18:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T00:31:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ef053586915d2ab0e2380f5b39f312515326a0f6","tid":2251384,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T18:25:28.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】控方昨確認本案中一名越南籍男學生被告黃臨福為早前潛逃台灣的「送中12人」之一，現正被內地當局拘留，昨日在他缺席下提到其角色，除指他有份掟汽油彈，更指他與一不知名人士在WhatsApp對話時，表明縱火是殺警為「手足」報仇。<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，案件首次在裁判法院提堂時，辯方向法庭投訴，指警員拘捕黃後恐嚇要將他「打死」、要求他唱「願榮光歸警察」、向他表示「最憎越南人，法官最憎越南人，判得你更重」，更要脅拘捕他全家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201021/MZSRE45IHJAQVJYCCXW2UBSZCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201021%2FMZSRE45IHJAQVJYCCXW2UBSZCQ%2F&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=049bb7f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201021%2FMZSRE45IHJAQVJYCCXW2UBSZCQ%2F&h=e83e81e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201021/MZSRE45IHJAQVJYCCXW2UBSZCQ/</a>"},{"pid":"367be2c745baf792a2d0327284937faa31d0e324","tid":2251384,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T18:26:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7970406e2da2e105bc7e959f04f52cf10efbac","tid":2251384,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T18:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal